data.text:
Four teams play in the Women’s Southern Conference: 1. SC Tempish Vitkovice and FBC Ostrava from the Czech Republic and Zug United and Kloten-Dietlikon Jets from Switzerland.

Zug United

Describe your team, and what we should expect from your team during Champions Cup 2024?

We are a quite young team filled with top class players bringing the maturity and experience, making us a great mix of people. The team is hungry for success and ready to fight for silverware from the first to the last second.

Players to watch

Team rookie or young player to look out for on your team and why?

#6 Emma Hedlund With some hard work, she can become a top goalscorer one day.

Who is a leader on and off the field and why?

#24 Denisa Ratajová She is one of the best players in the world and a strong character in the dressing room. The team respects her a lot and she inspires the team to follow her lead.

Most skillful player?

#21 Corin Rüttimann Her technique, precision and game intelligence make her scary for any opponent.

Which player demonstrates #FairFloorball the best?

#23 Isabelle Gerig Shows what this sport is about on and off the field. A true professional, always leading by example.

1. SC Tempish Vitkovice

Describe your team, and what we should expect from your team during Champions Cup 2024?

Our biggest strength is our specific mindset. We are always one consistent group, committed to the common goal. We are aware of our strengths and what we are able to do. During the Champions Cup 2024, you can always expect the unexpected.

Players to watch

Team rookie or young player to look out for on your team and why?

#11 Tereza Matýsková – young and skilled defender participated at the WFC WU19 2022 even before her very first Extraleague match.

Who is a leader on and off the field and why?

#22 Sára Seevaldová – experienced forward posses all important skills in order to get both, on and also off ways of our team in the right direction

Most skillful player?

#4 Michaela Kubečková – despite her young age she belongs to the experienced part of our team. Every team has to be aware of her skills.

Which player demonstrates #FairFloorball the best?

#3 Michaela Šponiarová – the most experienced player of our team, already legend of Vítkovice as well as Slovak Floorball. Michaela knows how to keep her playing level consistent

FBC Ostrava

Describe your team, and what we should expect from your team during Champions Cup 2024?

FBC Ostrava is an ambitious team from city of Ostrava. We worked really hard to climb our way to the top of Czech first division, where we belong. Our goal for this CC season is definitely advancing to the next stage and then do everything in our power to make it to the final tournament!

Players to watch

Team rookie or young player to look out for on your team and why?

Hard to choose one, but if we have to, it’s #71 Karolína Bínová She is 19 years old and an exciting talent.

Who is a leader on and off the field and why?

#5 Markéta Vrlíková is the on field leader, first of all she is the newly elected captain and also she’s been in FBC Ostrava for more than 10 years now. Off field leader is, apart from Markéta, #75 Veronika Tomšová, who is our first goalie. Whole team looks up to her and her word is sacred.

Most skillful player?

#99 Paulína Hudáková, Slovak defender with incredible skill. Her dekes and dribbling troubles players both in league and international matches.

Which player demonstrates #FairFloorball the best?

#9 Veronika Rybičková

Kloten-Dietlikon Jets

Describe your team, and what we should expect from your team during Champions Cup 2024?

The Kloten-Dietlikon Jets are a physically strong team made up of a mix of young talented and older experienced players. They all have one thing in common: they are hungry for success and don’t easily settle.

Players to watch

Team rookie or young player to look out for on your team and why?

#7 Laila Ediz Great ballhandling skills, smart and a good view.

Who is a leader on and off the field and why?

#5 Andrea Gämperli. Very experienced and skillful player showing a positive example.

Most skillful player?

#37 Linn Larsson

Which player demonstrates #FairFloorball the best?
